      <title>受油价和中国轮换风险影响，印度卢比面临缓慢下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/indian-rupee-faces-slow-grind-lower-on-oil-china-rotation-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度卢比兑美元汇率本月跌破 84，创下新低。由于地缘政治风险推高油价，以及资金转向中国导致本土股市流出，印度卢比汇率呈下跌趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/indian-rupee-faces-slow-grind-lower-on-oil-china-rotation-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 02:40:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
